trans-unit.source: Encapsulates a <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.
trans-unit.target: Encapsula um <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> is a simple class that encapsulates a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> for efficiency.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> é uma classe simple que encapsula uma <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> para maior eficiência.

trans-unit.source: By having a single class that is always loaded, you can defer the loading of the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> until it is needed.
trans-unit.target: Por ter uma única classe sempre é carregada, você pode adiar o carregamento de <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> até que seja necessário.

trans-unit.source: Because new classes can be derived from <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>, you could load a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> that could, in turn, load an assembly that is not already in memory.
trans-unit.target: Porque novas classes podem derivar de <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>, você pode carregar um <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> que poderia, por sua vez, carregar um assembly que não esteja na memória.

trans-unit.source: For a large collection of <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> objects, this could cause a large number of assemblies to be loaded, which decreases performance.
trans-unit.target: Para uma grande coleção de <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> objetos, isso pode causar um grande número de assemblies a serem carregados, o que reduz o desempenho.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the toolbox service deals only with <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objects and retrieves their contained <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> only when necessary.
trans-unit.target: Em vez disso, o serviço de caixa de ferramentas lida apenas com <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objetos e recupera seus independente <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> somente quando necessário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> is designed to hold any cached data from the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> foi projetado para manter os dados armazenados em cache do <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation only holds the filter of the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>, but deriving classes may choose to cache the name, image, and other information.
trans-unit.target: A implementação padrão só mantém o filtro do <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>, mas derivando de classes pode optar por armazenar em cache o nome, imagem e outras informações.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objects support two forms of serialization: they can be serialized through standard runtime serialization, and they can also load and save themselves from a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.IDataObject?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objetos dão suporte a duas formas de serialização: podem ser serializados por meio de serialização de tempo de execução padrão, e também pode carregar e salvar-se de um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.IDataObject?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The former provides a very easy way to save <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objects to a persistent storage.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro fornece uma maneira muito fácil salvar <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objetos para um armazenamento persistente.

trans-unit.source: The latter provides a way to integrate <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objects with mixed data storage formats.
trans-unit.target: O segundo fornece uma maneira para integrar <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemContainer> objetos com formatos de armazenamento de dados mistos.
